{"view":"article","slug":"f2l-naming","category":"3x3","subcategory":null,"topDir":"3x3","title":{"en":"F2L Naming","zh":"F2L命名"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">F2L Naming</strong></p><p>Useful in team BLD. Order: simple to difficult naming.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image3.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">A+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image5.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">A-</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">B+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image9.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">B-</strong></p></td><td><p>Very first letters in alphabet denote very first cases to learn. A,B also appear in a <a href=\"/alg/vhls\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">VHLS</a> naming method.</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image11.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>J+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image13.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>J-</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image15.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>L+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image17.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>L-</strong></p></td><td><p>J/L-shape</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image19.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>O<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image21.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">F</strong></p></td><td><p>Solved</p><p>Flip</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image23.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">E+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image25.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">E-</strong></p></td><td><p>E-Slice</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image27.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">U+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image29.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">U-</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image31.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">V+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image33.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">V-</strong></p></td><td><p>Twist in U. Then flip to get <a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>-V.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image35.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">D+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image37.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">D-</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image39.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">C+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image41.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">C-</strong></p></td><td><p>Twisty corner in D. Then flip to get <a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>-C.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image43.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">S</strong></p></td><td><p>Sexy. Alg (U R U' R')3 is Triple Unsexy.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image45.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">T</strong></p></td><td><p>Tower</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image47.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>I+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image49.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>I-</strong></p></td><td><p>I-shape</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image51.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>X+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image53.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>X-</strong></p></td><td><p>Checker</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image55.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>P+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image57.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>P-</strong></p></td><td><p>P+ has P-shape. Ignoring AUF, the 2nd move is a quarter turn, e.g., P+ alg U2 (R <strong>U</strong> R' U) R U' R'.</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image59.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Q+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image61.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Q-</strong></p></td><td><p>Q+ has Q-shape. Ignoring AUF, the 2nd move is a half turn, e.g., Q+ alg U (R <strong>U2'</strong> R' U) R U' R'.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image63.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>R+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image65.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>R-</strong></p></td><td><p>Analogy to the recognition pieces on R perms.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image67.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">K+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image69.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">K-</strong></p></td><td><p>Quick. The fastest non-free <a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image71.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">G+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image73.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">G-</strong></p></td><td><p>Analogy. G perms are very complicated, so do <a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>-G.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image75.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">H+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image77.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">H-</strong></p></td><td><p>Remove Sexy in <a href=\"/alg/oll\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">OLL</a>-H alg (R U2' R' U') (R U R' U') R U' R' to get F2L-H+ alg (R U2' R' U') R U R'.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image79.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">W+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image81.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">W-</strong></p></td><td><p>Wide Turn. W- alg = U' r U' (R' U R U) r'.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image83.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">M+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image85.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">M-</strong></p></td><td><p>Similar letters W,M denote similar cases. For EO control, M+ alg = (M' U' M U2) r U' r', M- alg = U' (R U' M' U') (R' U R U r').</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>List</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk53168601\"></a><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image3.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image5.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image9.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image89.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image91.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image67.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image69.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>A+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>A-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>K+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>K-</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image94.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image96.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image79.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image81.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image83.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image85.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image100.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image102.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>X+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>X-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>W+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>W-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>M+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>M-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>P+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>P-</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image104.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image106.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image75.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image77.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image109.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image111.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image71.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image73.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Q+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Q-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>H+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>H-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>I+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>I-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>G+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>G-</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image23.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image25.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image115.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image117.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image119.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image121.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image43.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image45.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>E+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>E-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>J+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>J-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>S</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>T</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image27.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image29.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image31.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image33.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image35.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image37.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image39.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image41.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>U+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>U-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>V+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>V-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>D+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>D-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>C+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>C-</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image21.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/en/image19.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>F</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>O</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>","zh":"<p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">F2L命名</strong></p><p>可用于合作盲拧. 顺序: 简单到困难命名.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image3.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">A+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image5.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">A-</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">B+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image9.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">B-</strong></p></td><td><p>字母表里最开头字母对应最开始学的情况. A,B也出现在<a href=\"/alg/vhls\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">VHLS</a>的一种命名里.</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image11.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>J+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image13.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>J-</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image15.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>L+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image17.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>L-</strong></p></td><td><p>J和L形</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image19.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>O<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image21.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">F</strong></p></td><td><p>还原态</p><p>Flip (翻棱)</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image23.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">E+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image25.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">E-</strong></p></td><td><p>E层</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image27.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">U+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image29.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">U-</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image31.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">V+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image33.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">V-</strong></p></td><td><p>U层转角. 再翻棱得到<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>-V.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image35.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">D+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image37.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">D-</strong></p><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image39.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">C+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image41.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">C-</strong></p></td><td><p>D层转角. 再翻棱得到<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>-C.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image43.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">S</strong></p></td><td><p>Sexy. 公式(U R U' R')3是三遍Unsexy.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image45.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">T</strong></p></td><td><p>Tower (塔)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image47.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>I+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image49.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>I-</strong></p></td><td><p>I形</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image51.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>X+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image53.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>X-</strong></p></td><td><p>Checker (棋盘)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image55.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>P+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image57.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>P-</strong></p></td><td><p>P+有p形. 忽略AUF, 公式第二步是90°转动, 例如P+公式U2 (R <strong>U</strong> R' U) R U' R'.</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image59.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Q+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image61.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Q-</strong></p></td><td><p>Q+有q形. 忽略AUF, 公式第二步是180°转动, 例如Q+公式U (R <strong>U2'</strong> R' U) R U' R'.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image63.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>R+</strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image65.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>R-</strong></p></td><td><p>类比R perm的观察点.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image67.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">K+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image69.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">K-</strong></p></td><td><p>Quick (快速). 最快的非基态<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image71.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">G+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image73.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">G-</strong></p></td><td><p>类比. G perm很复杂, <a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>-G也是.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image75.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">H+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image77.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">H-</strong></p></td><td><p>类比. 去掉<a href=\"/alg/oll\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">OLL</a>-H公式(R U2' R' U') (R U R' U') R U' R'中间的Sexy得到F2L-H+公式(R U2' R' U') R U R'.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image79.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">W+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image81.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">W-</strong></p></td><td><p>Wide Turn (双层转动). W'公式U' r U' (R' U R U) r'. </p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image83.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">M+<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image85.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">M-</strong></p></td><td><p>形状相似的字母W,M表示相似<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>; 另外, F2L-M分别有控棱公式(M' U' M U2) r U' r', U' (R U' M' U') (R' U R U r').</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>列表</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk53168601\"></a><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image3.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image5.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image9.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image89.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image91.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image67.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/f2l-naming/zh/image69.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></str